OL,3,CParents in Surrey are being urged not
OL,4,Cto buy smartphones for their children
OL,6,FHeadteachers from all of Surrey's 58
OL,7,Fsecondary schools have joined forces
OL,8,Fto urge parents of primary school
OL,9,Fchildren to not buy smartphones.
OL,11,FIt's part of the 'Smartphone Free
OL,12,FChildhood', a movement of over 350,000
OL,13,Ffamilies standing together to
OL,14,Fcollectively delay using phones and
OL,15,Fsocial media.
OL,17,FA letter was sent from Surrey
OL,18,FSecondary Phase Council urging
OL,19,Ffamilies to not buy mobile phones
OL,20,Funtil age 14 and no social media until
OL,21,F16.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
