OL,3,CParents in Surrey are being urged not
OL,4,Cto buy smartphones for their children
OL,6,FIt was intended for families of pupils
OL,7,Fin Years 4, 5 and 6 who are preparing
OL,8,Ffor the transition from primary to
OL,9,Fsecondary school.
OL,11,FSchools across Surrey say that they
OL,12,Fare increasingly seeing a negative
OL,13,Fimpact on young peoples wellbeing,
OL,14,Fsleep and readiness to learn because
OL,15,Fof smartphone use.
OL,17,FReal world social interaction is being
OL,18,Freplaced by children spending more
OL,19,Ftime online.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
