OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773162679
OL,3,CParents in Surrey are being urged not
OL,4,Cto buy smartphones for their children
OL,6,FInstead, it says there are "a
OL,7,Fsignificant number of occasions where
OL,8,Fsmartphone use has fractured a child
OL,9,For teenagers experience growing up".
OL,11,FAccording to Surrey Secondary Phase
OL,12,FCouncil, more parents and children
OL,13,Fregret allowing smartphone ownership
OL,14,Fand see it as having a high level of
OL,15,Fimpact on their family life.
OL,17,FSmartphone Free Childhood is
OL,18,Fencouraging parents to "delay, delay,
OL,19,Fdelay" phone ownership and social
OL,20,Fmedia.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
