PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773162679
OL,3,CParents in Surrey are being urged not
OL,4,Cto buy smartphones for their children
OL,6,FIt wants families to follow the
OL,7,F"parent pact", a collective agreement
OL,8,Fof when to give children access to
OL,9,Fphones:
OL,11,FSurrey is one of several London
OL,12,Fboroughs that has shown support for
OL,13,Fthe movement. Other boroughs where
OL,14,Fschools are getting involved include
OL,15,FBarnet, Enfield and Southwark.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
